            class="- topic/topic concept/concept ">
		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">22.810</ph> Solicitation provisions and contract clauses.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <ol id="d1359e13" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1373e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            When a contract is contemplated that will include the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1055793.dita#i1055793"
                        base="i1055793"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.222-26</xref>, Equal Opportunity, the contracting officer shall insert-</p>
					          <ol id="d1359e26" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d1373e30" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The clause at <xref href="FAR-i1055713.dita#i1055713"
                              base="i1055713"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.222-21</xref>, Prohibition of Segregated Facilities, in the solicitation and contract; and</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d1373e42" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The provision at <xref href="FAR-i1055729.dita#i1055729"
                              base="i1055729"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.222-22</xref>, Previous Contracts and Compliance Reports, in the solicitation.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1373e56" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The contracting officer shall insert the provision at <xref href="FAR-i1055741.dita#i1055741"
                        base="i1055741"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.222-23</xref>, Notice of Requirement for Affirmative Action to Ensure Equal Employment Opportunity for Construction, in solicitations for construction when a contract is contemplated that will include the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1055793.dita#i1055793"
                        base="i1055793"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.222-26</xref>, Equal Opportunity, and the amount of the contract is expected to be in excess of $10,000.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1373e71" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The contracting officer shall insert the provision at <xref href="FAR-i1055773.dita#i1055773"
                        base="i1055773"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.222-24</xref>, Preaward On-Site Equal Opportunity Compliance Evaluation, in solicitations other than those for construction when a contract is contemplated that will include the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1055793.dita#i1055793"
                        base="i1055793"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.222-26</xref>, Equal Opportunity, and the amount of the contract is expected be $10 million or more.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1373e86" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The contracting officer shall insert the provision at <xref href="FAR-i1055782.dita#i1055782"
                        base="i1055782"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.222-25</xref>, Affirmative Action Compliance, in solicitations, other than those for construction, when a contract is contemplated that will include the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1055793.dita#i1055793"
                        base="i1055793"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.222-26</xref>, Equal Opportunity.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1373e101" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(e)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The contracting officer shall insert the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1055793.dita#i1055793"
                        base="i1055793"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.222-26</xref>, Equal Opportunity, in solicitations and contracts (see <xref href="FAR-i1097248.dita#i1097248"
                        base="i1097248"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">22.802</xref>) unless the contract is exempt from all of the requirements of E.O.11246 (see <xref href="FAR-i1097315.dita#i1097315"
                        base="i1097315"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">22.807</xref>(a)). If the contract is exempt from one or more, but not all, of the requirements of E.O.11246, the contracting officer shall use the clause with its Alternate I.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1373e120" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(f)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The contracting officer shall insert the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1055834.dita#i1055834"
                        base="i1055834"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.222-27</xref>, Affirmative Action Compliance Requirements for Construction, in solicitations and contracts for construction that will include the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1055793.dita#i1055793"
                        base="i1055793"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.222-26</xref>, Equal Opportunity, when the amount of the contract is expected to be in excess of $10,000.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1373e135" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(g)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The contracting officer shall insert the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1055899.dita#i1055899"
                        base="i1055899"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.222-29</xref>, Notification of Visa Denial, in contracts that will include the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1055793.dita#i1055793"
                        base="i1055793"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.222-26</xref>, Equal Opportunity, if the contractor is required to perform in or on behalf of a foreign country.</p>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
